node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Saint Hoax on August 02, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Mrs. Betty Bowers @BettyBowers I've lost some respect for Matt Damon for two reasons: 1. Being a 51-year-old Harvard-educated person who only realized using homophobic slurs was a bad thing *months* ago; and 2. Being foolish enough to think that was a cute story he should share with the world.'.
Photo by Saint Hoax on August 02, 2021. May be an image of one or more people, people standing and text that says 'Saint Hoax @SaintHoax Matt Damon's daughter d literally STOP BEING HOMOPHOBIC'.
